        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It all depends on the case. I ought to think about that, before I give a definite answer, but the disciplinary code has been fairly worked out by all the parties concerned, and fairly administered. I do not think I ought to go further.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
